lass=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advantages 1. You can create your own characters without painting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different from traditional pixel painting tools, you should first draw characters yourself, and then make character animation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In [Px2d], you don't need to paint, and you don't need any painting experience. You can create your own character. [Px2d] Relying on the huge material library, there are a lot of materials for users to choose from. Just choose the materials you like, and you can create your own role. <br>Customize your role as you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support importing user-defined materials</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the materials in the material library, [Px2d] also supports users to import their own materials for animation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Advantages 2. Say goodbye to a single template and create unlimited possibilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different from the traditional paper doll system, there is only one single fixed action template. Because the action is fixed and cannot be adjusted, it cannot meet our demand for action.  <br>[Px2d] adopts the role body component mode. Every part of a character's body is a component. It can be adjusted at will. In this way, we can meet the needs of our actions to the greatest extent. If you want to do something, you can do it yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to provide maximum convenience for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The 2.0 version of Px2d has upgraded its built-in action library, which includes 82 types of actions. It includes combat actions and life actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/f0c3a5f30400f506c8817f1b2b55fa6b.mp4?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.poster.avif?t=1732018555\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.webm?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255310/extras/55268b21b60d8b849fa05752850fd2e2.mp4?t=1732018555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Advantages 3. One click export, greatly improving efficiency</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Px2d] Support one click to export png format pictures. No matter you have made any changes to the character style or the character action, you can export the resource with one click.</p>",
